runtimeAttrs.SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT
    source,
    companydesc,
    lobdesc,
    riskstate,
    a.annual_statement_line,
    stateline,
    directwrittenpremium,
    cededwrittenpremium,
    directunearnedpremium,
    cededunearnedpremium,
    directlosspaid,
    directcasereserve,
    directlossibnrreserve,
    cededlosspaid,
    cededcasereserve,
    cededlossibnrreserve,
    directpaiddcc,
    directpaidao,
    directlaecasreserve,
    directlaeibnrreserve,
    cededpaiddcc,
    cededpaidao,
    cededlaecasreserve,
    cededlaeibnrreserve,
    directcommissionsincurred,
    cededcommissionsincurred,
    account_entered_dt,
    reinsurancecompany
FROM (
    SELECT
        'PMS_Ceded_Premiums' AS source,
        CASE
            WHEN company_desc IS NULL THEN 'Merrimack'
            ELSE company_desc
        END AS companydesc,
        CASE
            WHEN stateline = '1' THEN 'Fire'
            WHEN stateline = '2' THEN 'Extended Coverage (EC)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('A', '4', '6', '7') THEN 'Homeowner (HO)'
            WHEN stateline = '9' THEN 'Inland Marine (IM)'
            WHEN stateline = 'X' AND TRIM(m.dim_key) LIKE '017' THEN 'Personal Umbrella (PUMB)'
            WHEN stateline = 'X' AND TRIM(m.dim_key) LIKE '617' THEN 'Commercial Umbrella (CUMB)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('8', 'D', 'C') THEN 'Business Owners Policy (BOP)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('E', '5') THEN 'Commercial Multi Peril (CMP)'
            WHEN stateline = 'Y' THEN 'Dwelling Liability'
        END AS lobdesc,
        s.gen4_desc AS riskstate,
        annual_statement_line,
        stateline,
        NULL AS directwrittenpremium,
        SUM(COALESCE(ceded_premium, 0)) AS cededwrittenpremium,
        NULL AS directunearnedpremium,
        NULL AS cededunearnedpremium,
        NULL AS directlosspaid,
        NULL AS directcasereserve,
        NULL AS directlossibnrreserve,
        NULL AS cededlosspaid,
        NULL AS cededcasereserve,
        NULL AS cededlossibnrreserve,
        NULL AS directpaiddcc,
        NULL AS directpaidao,
        NULL AS directlaecasreserve,
        NULL AS directlaeibnrreserve,
        0 AS cededpaiddcc,
        0 AS cededpaidao,
        0 AS cededlaecasreserve,
        0 AS cededlaeibnrreserve,
        NULL AS directcommissionsincurred,
        SUM(f.commission_amount) AS cededcommissionsincurred,
        account_entered_dt AS account_entered_dt,
        reinsurance_code AS reinsurancecompany
    FROM dbo.pms_policy_reins_transaction f
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT
            policy_key AS master_policy_key,
            company_desc,
            COALESCE(r.lob_display_desc, 'Not Applicable') AS lob_desc,
           LPAD(module_number, 3, '0') AS module_number,
            i.fairplan_desc
        FROM dbo.pms_master_policy i
        LEFT JOIN dbo.lob_ref r ON r.pms_lob_desc = i.lob_desc
    ) p ON p.master_policy_key = f.policy_key
    LEFT JOIN dbo.hier_dim_riskstate s ON s.dim_id = f.risk_state_id
    LEFT JOIN dbo.profitloss_factors_ref ref ON ref.state_line_code = f.stateline
        AND ref.year = CASE
            WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM f.account_entered_dt) <= 2019 THEN 2019
            ELSE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM f.account_entered_dt)
        END
    LEFT JOIN dbo.hier_dim_majorperil m ON m.dim_id = f.major_peril_id
    WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM f.account_entered_dt) >= 2005
        AND UPPER(TRIM(p.fairplan_desc)) = 'NO'
    GROUP BY
        company_desc,
        reinsurance_code,
        CASE
            WHEN stateline = '1' THEN 'Fire'
            WHEN stateline = '2' THEN 'Extended Coverage (EC)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('A', '4', '6', '7') THEN 'Homeowner (HO)'
            WHEN stateline = '9' THEN 'Inland Marine (IM)'
            WHEN stateline = 'X' AND TRIM(m.dim_key) LIKE '017' THEN 'Personal Umbrella (PUMB)'
            WHEN stateline = 'X' AND TRIM(m.dim_key) LIKE '617' THEN 'Commercial Umbrella (CUMB)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('8', 'D', 'C') THEN 'Business Owners Policy (BOP)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('E', '5') THEN 'Commercial Multi Peril (CMP)'
            WHEN stateline = 'Y' THEN 'Dwelling Liability'
        END,
        account_entered_dt,
        s.gen4_desc,
        annual_statement_line,
        stateline
    UNION
    SELECT
        'PMS_Ceded_Losses' AS source,
        CASE
            WHEN company_desc IS NULL THEN 'Merrimack'
            ELSE company_desc
        END AS companydesc,
        CASE
            WHEN stateline = '1' THEN 'Fire'
            WHEN stateline = '2' THEN 'Extended Coverage (EC)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('A', '4', '6', '7') THEN 'Homeowner (HO)'
            WHEN stateline = '9' THEN 'Inland Marine (IM)'
            WHEN stateline = 'X' AND TRIM(m.dim_key) LIKE '017' THEN 'Personal Umbrella (PUMB)'
            WHEN stateline = 'X' AND TRIM(m.dim_key) LIKE '617' THEN 'Commercial Umbrella (CUMB)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('8', 'D', 'C') THEN 'Business Owners Policy (BOP)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('E', '5') THEN 'Commercial Multi Peril (CMP)'
            WHEN stateline = 'Y' THEN 'Dwelling Liability'
        END AS lobdesc,
        s.gen4_desc AS riskstate,
        annual_statement_line,
        stateline,
        NULL AS directwrittenpremium,
        NULL AS cededwrittenpremium,
        NULL AS directunearnedpremium,
        NULL AS cededunearnedpremium,
        NULL AS directlosspaid,
        NULL AS directcasereserve,
        NULL AS directlossibnrreserve,
        SUM(loss_paid_amt) AS cededlosspaid,
        SUM(loss_paid_amt) AS cededcasereserve,
        0 AS cededlossibnrreserve,
        NULL AS directpaiddcc,
        NULL AS directpaidao,
        NULL AS directlaecasreserve,
        NULL AS directlaeibnrreserve,
        SUM(loss_alae_expense) AS cededpaiddcc,
        SUM(loss_ulae_expense) AS cededpaidao,
        0 AS cededlaecasreserve,
        0 AS cededlaeibnrreserve,
        NULL AS directcommissionsincurred,
        NULL AS cededcommissionsincurred,
        account_entered_dt AS account_entered_dt,
        reinsurance_code AS reinsurancecompany
    FROM dbo.pms_reins_fact_loss f
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT
            policy_key AS master_policy_key,
            company_desc,
            COALESCE(r.lob_display_desc, 'Not Applicable') AS lob_desc,
            LPAD(module_number, 3, '0') AS module_number,
            i.fairplan_desc
        FROM dbo.pms_master_policy i
        LEFT JOIN dbo.lob_ref r ON r.pms_lob_desc = i.lob_desc
    ) p ON p.master_policy_key = f.policy_key
    LEFT JOIN dbo.hier_dim_riskstate s ON s.dim_id = f.risk_state_id
    LEFT JOIN dbo.profitloss_factors_ref ref ON ref.state_line_code = f.stateline
        AND ref.year = CASE
            WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM f.account_entered_dt) <= 2019 THEN 2019
            ELSE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM f.account_entered_dt)
        END
    LEFT JOIN dbo.hier_dim_majorperil m ON m.dim_id = f.majorperilid
    WHERE UPPER(TRIM(p.fairplan_desc)) = 'NO'
    GROUP BY
        company_desc,
        reinsurance_code,
        CASE
            WHEN stateline = '1' THEN 'Fire'
            WHEN stateline = '2' THEN 'Extended Coverage (EC)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('A', '4', '6', '7') THEN 'Homeowner (HO)'
            WHEN stateline = '9' THEN 'Inland Marine (IM)'
            WHEN stateline = 'X' AND TRIM(m.dim_key) LIKE '017' THEN 'Personal Umbrella (PUMB)'
            WHEN stateline = 'X' AND TRIM(m.dim_key) LIKE '617' THEN 'Commercial Umbrella (CUMB)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('8', 'D', 'C') THEN 'Business Owners Policy (BOP)'
            WHEN stateline IN ('E', '5') THEN 'Commercial Multi Peril (CMP)'
            WHEN stateline = 'Y' THEN 'Dwelling Liability'
        END,
        account_entered_dt,
        s.gen4_desc,
        annual_statement_line,
        stateline
) a
ORDER BY a.account_entered_dt
